OL,7,FJennie Henry was at the memorial for
OL,8,Fan LNER officer killed during an air
OL,9,Fraid in York 82 years ago to the day
OL,11,FA headstone has been unveiled for a
OL,12,Fpolice officer who died during a
OL,13,FSecond World War air raid more than 80
OL,14,Fyears after he was laid to rest in an
OL,15,Funmarked grave.
OL,17,FLNER railway police constable Robert
OL,18,FSmith was killed during the Baedeker
OL,19,Fair raid in York during the early
OL,20,Fhours of 29 April 1942.
