OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FMr Smith, who served at York Railway
OL,8,FStation during the war, was among 94
OL,9,Fpeople who were killed in the raid.
OL,11,FHundreds more were injured in
OL,12,FLuftwaffe raids which hit historic
OL,13,Ftargets, with York one of five England
OL,14,Fcathedral cities bombed.
OL,16,FThe raid saw three platforms destroyed
OL,17,Fand caused paraffin used to light the
OL,18,Fstation to go up in flames, engulfing
OL,19,Fthe parcel office where Mr Smith was
OL,20,Fon duty.
