OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FMembers of that group, along with
OL,8,Frepresentatives of LNER, the 'Raids
OL,9,FOver York' heritage project, and
OL,10,FNormandy veteran Ken Cooke, came
OL,11,Ftogether for the ceremony today, where
OL,12,Fa wreath was laid at the site of the
OL,13,Fnew headstone.
OL,15,FDavid Horne, managing director at
OL,16,FLNER, said: "With no family of his own
OL,17,Fhaving been located, to see Robert
OL,18,FSmith's railway family come together
OL,19,Ffor his memorial service ensures that
OL,20,Fwe will never forget his immense
OL,21,Fcourage and bravery.
