OL,3,CPolice officer given marked grave 82
OL,4,Cyears after being killed in WW2 air
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,F"There is now a lasting memorial to a
OL,8,Fdedicated LNER colleague and family
OL,9,Fman, who sacrificed his own life to
OL,10,Fsave others."
OL,12,FMr Cooke, who served with the Green
OL,13,FHowards, said: "It's really important
OL,14,Fwe recognise these civilian people who
OL,15,Fdid brave deeds. I' m very honoured to
OL,16,Fbe part of that ceremony."
