OL,5,Craid
OL,7,FHe added: "You must keep going as long
OL,8,Fas you can to remember the things that
OL,9,Fhappened and those people who gave
OL,10,Ftheir lives. We must never forget, and
OL,11,Fa headstone to Robert Smith makes sure
OL,12,Fthat he will never be forgotten."
OL,14,FNick Beilby, from the Raids Over York
OL,15,Fheritage project, said: "Through our
OL,16,Fwork on the Raids Over York project,
OL,17,Fwe were interested to discover more
OL,18,Fabout Robert Smith and the role that
OL,19,Fhe played on the night of 29 April
OL,20,F1942.
