OL,3,CPolice officer given marked grave 82
OL,4,Cyears after being killed in WW2 air
OL,5,Craid
OL,7,F"For him to be recognised and
OL,8,Fmemorialised is testament to his
OL,9,Fbravery and sacrifice and something of
OL,10,Fwhich we are immensely proud."
OL,12,FJohn Owen, BTP History Group, said:
OL,13,F"Robert's story was first uncovered
OL,14,Fwhen researching the Roll of Honour of
OL,15,Ffallen railway police officers. When
OL,16,Fwe realised he had received very
OL,17,Flittle recognition, we worked on
OL,18,Ffinding out more about his life.
